# Extracted assets under web/public/ are regenerated by tools/extract-*.mjs
# out of SWING/. Committing them there would bloat the repo.
#
# NOTE: the root-level `assets/`, `build/` and `index.html` ARE committed
# on purpose — they are the Vite build output that GitHub Pages serves.
# See README.md § "How to refresh the deployment".
web/public/assets/sfx/
web/public/assets/backgrounds/
web/public/assets/sprites/
web/public/assets/music/

# Reverse-engineering scratch output
docs/wippe-candidates/

# Vite / node
web/node_modules/
web/dist/
web/.vite/
*.log

# Dashboard (local Piano Analytics + Google Sheets dashboard)
dashboard/node_modules/
dashboard/dist/
dashboard/dist-server/
dashboard/data/
dashboard/.env
dashboard/.vite/
